/uploads/2023/01/ReunionesEstatales.03.jpg 700w, https://presidente.gob.mx/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/ReunionesEstatales.03-300x102.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px" /></a></div><div id="media_image-14" class="widget widget_media_image"><a href="https://programasparaelbienestar.gob.mx/mapa-banco-del-bienestar-sucursales-retiros/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img width="700" height="238" src="https://presidente.gob.mx/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/Banners_Portal_Presi_Banco_700x238.png" class="image wp-image-153137  attachment-700x238 size-700x238" alt="" loading="lazy" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto;" srcset="https://presidente.gob.mx/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/Banners_Portal_Presi_Banco_700x238.png 700w, https://presidente.gob.mx/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/Banners_Portal_Presi_Banco_700x238-300x102.png 300w" sizes="(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px" /></a></div><div id="linkcat-3502" class="widget widget_links"><h3 class="widget-title">Enlaces de interés</h3>
